description: Lily Allen - It's Not Me, It's You (Bonus DVD) [2009] DVD5 Lily Rose Beatrice Cooper[1] (née Allen; born 2 May 1985), known professionally as Lily Allen, is an English singer, songwriter, actress, and television presenter. She is the daughter of actor Keith Allen and film producer Alison Owen. 2009 reissue UK Special Edition 2-disc [CD/DVD] (PAL/Region 0) album set that comprises a 21-track CD album plus a Bonus DVD containing gig footage filmed at the Shepherds Bush Empire earlier this year, a track-by-track interview with Lily about 'It's Not Me, It's You' and 4 music videos. Complete with revised artwork! EMI. 2009.
